---
/**
 * Theme Extensions Gallery
 *
 * Overview of all experimental theme extensions.
 */

import LabLayout from '../../../layouts/LabLayout.astro';
---

<LabLayout
  title="Theme Extensions"
  description="Experimental theme extensions for Vanilla Breeze: motion tokens, backgrounds, fonts, and more."
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/lab/">Lab</a> / <span aria-current="page">Theme Extensions</span>
  </nav>

  <h1>Theme Extensions</h1>
  <p class="lead">Exploring new capabilities for the Vanilla Breeze theme system.</p>

  <aside class="callout callout--info" style="margin-block-end: var(--size-l);">
    <strong>Now in Core:</strong> These extension tokens are included in Vanilla Breeze core (<code>src/tokens/extensions/</code>).
    See <a href="/docs/themes/#extensions">Theme Extensions documentation</a> for usage and token reference.
  </aside>

  <section>
    <h2>Available Extensions</h2>
    <layout-grid data-min="280px" data-gap="m">
      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/motion-tokens/" class="section-card">
        <h3>Motion Tokens</h3>
        <p>Hover effects, transition presets, staggered animations, and View Transitions API integration.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/backgrounds/" class="section-card">
        <h3>Backgrounds</h3>
        <p>Gradients, noise textures, glassmorphism, and animated backgrounds.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/rough-borders/" class="section-card">
        <h3>Rough Borders</h3>
        <p>SVG filters, border-image, and mask-image techniques for sketchy themes.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/custom-fonts/" class="section-card">
        <h3>Custom Fonts</h3>
        <p>Google Fonts, variable fonts, and font loading API patterns.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/sound-effects/" class="section-card">
        <h3>Sound Effects</h3>
        <p>Web Audio API experiments for UI feedback sounds.</p>
      </a>
    </layout-grid>
  </section>
</LabLayout>
